The 2nd beta of my first map. English description Ct's objective is to make reign order in the jail. Terro's objective is to kill CT's This is the first map I've made and of curse it's not a final version, lots of things can be improved. Tabs pointing out places are in french, sorry but I designed this map for french friends first. But that's okay, you should be able to translate without speaking any french word...by testing :P There are guns under some beds in jail, you only need to go on the bed to pick it. There's no water in ducts because I've put ladders instead ( and there's no water in an airduct, though)
